  "body": "```\r\npragma experimental SMTChecker;\r\n\r\ncontract C {\r\n  uint constant GWEI = 1e9;\r\n  function f() public payable {\r\n    uint tmp = msg.value / GWEI;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nresults in\r\n\r\n```\r\nWarning: Unused local variable.\r\n --> div.sol:6:5:\r\n  |\r\n6 |     uint tmp = msg.value / GWEI;\r\n  |     ^^^^^^^^\r\n\r\nWarning: Division by zero happens here\r\n --> div.sol:6:16:\r\n  |\r\n6 |     uint tmp = msg.value / GWEI;\r\n  |                ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\nNote:   for:\r\n  <result> = 0\r\n  GWEI = 0\r\n  msg.value = 0\r\n  tmp = 0\r\n\r\nNote: Callstack: \r\nNote: \r\n```",
